Level 0: Starts with a book explaining what they signed up for and the resources that are added
Level 1: Level one items are the gears, mining well, flood gate, redstone engine, item pipes
Level 2: Level two items gives player: combustion engine, tank, auto-crafting table, facades, fluid pipes
Level 3: Level three items gives player: Quarry, Iron engine, energy pipes, plugs
Level 4: Level four gives player: Lazers, assembly table, pipe wires, gates
level 5: Level 5 gives player: access to things to craft robots





If Addons such as Redstone Distortion and BCA are installed, limit the amount of categories these mods already have to these 6 categories for BC